  "logNo": "220041692107",
  "title": "불임과 보조생식술, 한방치료",
  "addDate": "2014. 6. 26.",
  "categoryNo": "24",
  "parentCategoryNo": "8",
  "url": "https://blog.naver.com/PostView.naver?blogId=isuhani&logNo=220041692107",
  "html_size": 188770,
  "body": "<div id=\"post-view220041692107\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea220041692107\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div style=\"font-size:10pt; font-family:'957317_10';\" class=\"view\"><p><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">&#65279;피임을 하지 않고 정상적인 성생활을 하면서 1년 내에 임신이 안되는 경우를 불임이라 한다. </span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">&#8203;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">불임치료를 위해 외래를 방문하는 커플의 수는 3배로 늘었다. &#8203;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">&#8203;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">&#8203;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">&#8203;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">불임의 일차적인 치료에는 </span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">&#8203;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">배란 유도(ovulation induction; OI), </span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">&#8203;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140626_147/isuhani_1403743126587ljPT4_JPEG/%B4%D9%BF%EE%B7%CE%B5%E5_%2811%29.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"192\" height=\"143\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 143px; rwidth: 192px;\" id=\"20140626_147/isuhani_1403743126587ljPT4_JPEG/%B4%D9%BF%EE%B7%CE%B5%E5_%2811%29.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000333B81C3CB')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140626_147/isuhani_1403743126587ljPT4_JPEG/%B4%D9%BF%EE%B7%CE%B5%E5_%2811%29.jpg?type=w3\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /></span><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">&#8203;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">&#8203;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">&#8203;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">자궁 내 정액주입(Intrauterine insemination; IUI),</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\"></span>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/be8ba634663ab733.jpg\" width=\"255\" height=\"198\" style=\"cursor: pointer;border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); rheight: 198px; rwidth: 255px;\" id=\"20140626_172/isuhani_1403743126495Fbjbd_JPEG/%B4%D9%BF%EE%B7%CE%B5%E5_%2812%29.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000333B81C3CB')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/be8ba634663ab733.jpg\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/3e87d6f0961a5426.jpg\" width=\"240\" height=\"185\" style=\"cursor: pointer;border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); rheight: 185px; rwidth: 240px;\" id=\"20140626_139/isuhani_14037431263308J6RU_JPEG/%B4%D9%BF%EE%B7%CE%B5%E5_%2813%29.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000333B81C3CB')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/3e87d6f0961a5426.jpg\"></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">&#8203;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">&#8203;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">&#8203;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">체외수정(In Vitro fertilization; IVF),</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">&#8203;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">&#8203;<img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140626_84/isuhani_1403743279610NVuVz_JPEG/IVF_%BA%B8%C1%B6%BB%FD%BD%C4%BC%FA_4.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"258\" height=\"196\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 196px; rwidth: 258px;\" id=\"20140626_84/isuhani_1403743279610NVuVz_JPEG/IVF_%BA%B8%C1%B6%BB%FD%BD%C4%BC%FA_4.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000333B81C3CB')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140626_84/isuhani_1403743279610NVuVz_JPEG/IVF_%BA%B8%C1%B6%BB%FD%BD%C4%BC%FA_4.jpg?type=w3\"></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">&#8203;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">&#8203;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">&#8203;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">난관 내 배우자 이식(Gamete Intrafallopian Transfer;GIFT),</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\"></span>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/17e3d9333bc54017.jpg\" width=\"165\" height=\"194\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 194px; rwidth: 165px;\" id=\"20140626_45/isuhani_1403743126194xLR0H_JPEG/%B4%D9%BF%EE%B7%CE%B5%E5_%2814%29.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000333B81C3CB')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/17e3d9333bc54017.jpg\"></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">&#8203;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">&#8203;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">&#8203;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">&#8203;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">난자 세포질 내 정자 주입(Intracytoplasmic Sperm Injection; ICSI),</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\"></span>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140626_88/isuhani_1403743126056QHQ65_JPEG/%B4%D9%BF%EE%B7%CE%B5%E5_%2815%29.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"240\" height=\"148\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 148px; rwidth: 240px;\" id=\"20140626_88/isuhani_1403743126056QHQ65_JPEG/%B4%D9%BF%EE%B7%CE%B5%E5_%2815%29.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000333B81C3CB')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140626_88/isuhani_1403743126056QHQ65_JPEG/%B4%D9%BF%EE%B7%CE%B5%E5_%2815%29.jpg?type=w3\"></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">&#8203;</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\"></span></span>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">&#8203;</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">그리고</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">&#8203;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">불임의 원인 및 부부의 체질에 맞춘 한약치료와 침뜸치료</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">&#8203;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">&#8203;<img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140626_188/isuhani_1403743335251aoky8_JPEG/imagesCAEH2V5M.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"240\" height=\"171\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 171px; rwidth: 240px;\" id=\"20140626_188/isuhani_1403743335251aoky8_JPEG/imagesCAEH2V5M.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000333B81C3CB')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140626_188/isuhani_1403743335251aoky8_JPEG/imagesCAEH2V5M.jpg?type=w3\"></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">&#8203;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">가 있다. </span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">&#8203;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">정상 출산 능력을 가진 커플에서 정상 가임율(fecundity rate)은 매월 20~25% 이다. </span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">&#8203;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">이는 커플의 80%가 12개월 내에 자연적으로 임신을 할 수 있고, 90%는 18개월 내에 임신을 할 수 있다는 의미이다. </span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">&#8203;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">나머지 10%의 커플은 이 기간동안 임신을 하지 못하는데, 이런 불임의 원인은 매우 다양하다. </span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">&#8203;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">불임에 대한 검사를 받은 커플 중 40%는 순수한 남성 요인이고, 40%는 순수한 여성 요인이며, 환자 집단의 10%는 양쪽 모두에 원인이 있다. 불임에 대한 검사가 끝난 시점에서 10%는 그 원인을 알 수 없다. </span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">&#8203;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">&#8203;<img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140626_267/isuhani_1403743126685ohuu0_JPEG/20140626_093147.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"317\" height=\"310\" style=\"cursor: pointer;border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);.05px; rheight: 310.05px; rwidth: 317px;\" id=\"20140626_267/isuhani_1403743126685ohuu0_JPEG/20140626_093147.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000333B81C3CB')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140626_267/isuhani_1403743126685ohuu0_JPEG/20140626_093147.jpg?type=w3\"></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">&#8203;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">&#8203;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">50%의 환자에서 하나 또는 그 이상의 원인을 파악할 수 있고, </span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">이런 경우,</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">적절한 치료에 의해 50%에서 임신이 가능하다. &#8203;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">&#8203;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">불임 커플을 효과적으로 치료하기 위해서는 여성 불임에 대한 검사와 남성 불임에 대한 검사를 동시에 시행할 필요가 있다. &#8203;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">&#8203;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">&#8203;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">보조생식술의 종류가 다양해지고, 기술이 발달하면서</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">불임에 대한 한방 치료도 그에 맞춰 변화하고 있다. </span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">&#8203;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">기존에는 불임인 경우 침뜸과 한약복용 만으로 치료를 해왔었다. </span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">&#8203;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">최근에는 보조생식술(인공수정, 체외수정 등)과 병행하면서</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">보조생식술의 성공률을 높이고, 시술과정에 나타나는 각종 부작용을 경감시켜주기위한</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">침치료 및 한약처방을 하는 비율도 점차 높아져가고 있다. </span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">&#8203;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">&#8203;</span></p></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
